summary: I've been watching Dan and Phil's Undertale gameplay (playthrough? Idk) as I've been dealing with some depression yay and I just...
body:
I’ve been watching Dan and Phil’s Undertale gameplay (playthrough? Idk) as I’ve been dealing with some depression yay and I just found myself crocheting a little Napstablook and then I wrapped them up in some Christmas lights to cheer them up 🎄

So, for those who don’t know, the Napstablook is part of the Undertale universe (and Undertale is coming out on the Switch which might be why I’m suddenly so excited about it)

Reasons to love Napstablook:

- the first time you meet them they pretend to be asleep by making a ZZZZZZZZ noise

- asks you to lay down with them and “feel like garbage together”

- makes CDs and asks you to listen to them

Also favorite quote “Really not feelin’ up to it right now. Sorry.” when they don’t want to fight you.

You can go give it a like on my Instagram 💕
